  m_Text: This shows you how the <color=#0FF>Tap To Select</color> and <color=#0FF>Transform</color>
    demo scenes can be combined. Each transform component has the <color=#0FF>Use
    / Required Selectable</color> setting, which will automatically be set if the
    current GameObject has the <color=#0FF>LeanSelectableByFinger</color> component,
    and only activate if the current object is selected.
